#('''deaf'''; {{compare}} [[deafer]], {{super}} [[deafest]]) Not having the faculty of [[hearing]], or only partially able to hear.
#('''Deaf'''; {{notcomp}}) When capitalized, of or relating to the culture surrounding deaf users of sign language.

